</XX>
<IN>P6719 Holding Companies, NEC.
    P2819 Industrial Inorganic Chemicals, NEC.
    P2879 Agricultural Chemicals, NEC.
    P2834 Pharmaceutical Preparations.
    P6726 Investment Offices, NEC.
